description: **OPEN HOUSE CANCELLED, an OFFER was Accepted...Step into the convenience of City Point living with this bi-level condo (866 SF), perfectly situated near the East Broadway shops & restaurants, M Street beach, and all bus lines. This 1+ bedroom, one bath unit, while in need of some cosmetic updating, offers a comfortable living space. The flexible layout, with two alcove rooms, allows for a second bedroom, a home office, or a large walk-in closet. Features include private laundry, roof rights, hardwood floors, and storage. The current owner is willing to update the kitchen and bath for the right price, ensuring you can enjoy the best of City Point living.
